# 🔁 Full Lifecycle Flow

```
NEW
 ↓ (start())
RUNNABLE
 ↓ (scheduler)
RUNNING
 ↓ ↓ ↓
WAITING / TIMED_WAITING / RUNNABLE
 ↓
RUNNING
 ↓
DEAD
```

